                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Où se posait sa main fluette,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Un murmure plaintif en sort.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La boîte à musique est muette ;\nMais, quand on pousse le ressort\nOù se posait sa main fluette,\nUn murmure plaintif en sort."
